---
import Layout from '../components/layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Us | Eliphany" description="Learn why we curate premium skin-care supplements and how to reach us on WhatsApp.">
  <section class="py-16 px-4 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">About Eliphany</h1>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 items-start">
      <div class="md:col-span-2 space-y-4 text-gray-700">
        <p>
          Eliphany was born from a simple belief: healthy, radiant skin should be
          accessible, honest, and fuss-free. We hand-pick science-backed supplements
          and serums that actually deliver—no 12-step routines, no empty promises.
        </p>
        <p>
          Every product you see here has been tested by our team, approved by
          dermatologists we trust, and priced transparently. No hidden fees, no
          middle-men—just message us on WhatsApp and we’ll handle the rest.
        </p>
        <p>
          Based in Dubai, we ship across the UAE within 24 h and reply to every
          WhatsApp query in under two hours (Mon-Sat, 9 am-6 pm).
        </p>
      </div>

      <figure class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg">
        <img
          src="https://picsum.photos/seed/about-portrait/400/500"
          alt="Founder portrait – replace this image"
          class="w-full h-full object-cover"
        />
      </figure>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 text-center">
      <a
        href="https://wa.me/971501234567?text=Hi! I’d like to know more about your products."
        class="btn-whatsapp inline-flex items-center gap-2"
      >
        <span>Chat with us on WhatsApp</span>
